Location coverage is checked against the official Tim Hortons U.S. directory. Menu categories are based on the U.S. ordering experience and official product announcements. Price examples are treated as guidance because a single restaurant chain can use different franchise, delivery and local-market pricing.

Every indexable state page includes a unique location summary, regional availability note, crawlable internal links, visible source methodology, FAQ content and structured data that matches the page text.', 'Tim Hortons Menu USA: Prices, Deals & Locations', 'Browse Tim Hortons menu prices, current deals and verified location coverage across 50 states, Washington, D.C., and Puerto Rico.', true, 'published') on conflict (route_path) do nothing;

Third-party coupon codes are not treated as verified unless the offer can also be confirmed through Tim Hortons. Personalized app offers may not appear for every account. Always check expiration dates, minimum spend, participating restaurants, service-mode restrictions and product exclusions.', 'Tim Hortons Deals, Coupons and Offers USA', 'Current Tim Hortons U.S. deals, coupons, app offers, value-menu pricing and seasonal promotions with terms and verification notes.', true, 'published') on conflict (route_path) do nothing;

This independent website helps U.S. customers understand menu categories, price variation, current promotional claims and location availability before opening a restaurant ordering screen.

## What makes a state page indexable

A state page becomes indexable only when verified location coverage exists. Pages without verified coverage remain accessible for users and internal navigation but use a noindex directive.

## Independence and trademarks

This site is not affiliated with Tim Hortons. Brand names and product marks belong to their respective owners. The site does not use official branding in a way that implies ownership or endorsement.', 'About This Independent Menu Guide', 'How the Tim Hortons Menu USA Guide researches prices, deals and official location coverage.', true, 'published') on conflict (route_path) do nothing;

Location coverage is checked against the official Tim Hortons U.S. location directory. New products and nationwide value offers are checked against official announcements and offer terms.

## Price methodology

Prices are labeled as official promotional prices, observed starting prices, or “check local store.” A delivery-platform price is not described as a guaranteed in-store or statewide price.

## Review dates and corrections

Every state page displays its review date. Closed locations, expired deals and incorrect prices should be corrected when identified.

## Scaled-page safeguards

Pages without verified location coverage use noindex. Active state pages combine unique city coverage, regional menu notes, current deal context, state-specific FAQs and source transparency.', 'Editorial and Update Policy', 'Sources, review dates, corrections and pricing methodology for this independent Tim Hortons menu guide.', true, 'published') on conflict (route_path) do nothing;

When you subscribe, the site stores your email address, optional preferred state, subscription date and active status. This data is used for menu and deal updates.

## Unsubscribe and deletion

Every newsletter should include an unsubscribe method. Subscriber records should be deleted or disabled promptly when requested.

## Analytics and advertising

The production site may use Google Analytics and Google AdSense when enabled by the administrator. Update this policy with the final consent, cookie and regional compliance details before monetization.', 'Privacy Policy', 'Privacy policy for email subscriptions, website analytics, advertising and technical logs.', true, 'published') on conflict (route_path) do nothing;

